## Build artifacts
artifacts/
packages/

## GoblinBench run output
## The canonical record (runs/goblinbench.sqlite) IS committed — it's the backup.
## On-disk run-* trees are ring-buffered scratch space (regenerable by re-running),
## gitignored so git history doesn't grow unboundedly with every run.
runs/*
!runs/.gitkeep
!runs/goblinbench.sqlite
## SQLite runtime files (WAL + shm) — never commit; the main .sqlite is current.
runs/goblinbench.sqlite-wal
runs/goblinbench.sqlite-shm
runs/goblinbench-results.sqlite
runs/goblinbench-results.sqlite-*

